g out with costs lower than initially estimated.\n\nFreight and MSC increased by about $262k due to the agreement with JGE for days in excess of the original freight paid for the expected voyage from HOU - RDJ - HOU. The voyage was 14 days longer than generated with about 9 of these being included in the additional freight, however there was some idle time at the end of the voyage for owner\u0027s matters. These days were also used for cleaning the tanks and preparing for the next voyage and therefore will not be for owner\u0027s account but reflected on voyage 2305 as the time was at RDJ before vessel fully sailed.\n\nLastly, bunkers increased quite a bit for this voyage due to the higher price on LSMGO. With the extended time in port, vessel could not reach Argentina with the amount ROB."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-09-28T14:19:21.527","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Days in excess amended to the final amount: 8.785 and cleaning costs accounted for in bunker cons."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-09-27T20:34:49.887","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Houston Port Costs less than generated"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-09-01T22:54:19.54","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Vsl anchored after discharging for vsl repairs and to clean her tanks simultaneously."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-08-24T13:43:13.517","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Maceio Port Costs lower than expected"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-08-22T16:18:05.06","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"53.89 total days"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-08-14T19:37:10.173","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Variable FW Surcharge for PC included in port costs due to ballast transit."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-08-14T12:53:02.28","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Bunkers higher than generated on laden passage"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-08-10T12:53:02.18","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Maceio Port costs higher than generated"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-07-28T15:22:41.597","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"PDA F